      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The newest models represent a significant leap. Kling V3 produces videos with better temporal consistency — meaning frames flow smoothly without jitter or sudden jumps. V3 Omni goes further by supporting multiple input modalities and delivering richer scene detail. If you tried an earlier version and were underwhelmed, the V3 generation will surprise you.",
