      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Both modes work exceptionally well. Text-to-video gives you creative freedom to describe any scene. Image-to-video is perfect when you have a specific visual starting point — say, a product photo or a character illustration — and want to add realistic motion to it. The AI respects the composition of the original image while introducing natural movement.",
