          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I do not believe in tearing tools down, but I do believe in honest context. The AI video space has matured rapidly. Tools like Runway, Pika, and Luma have all made impressive strides. Kling AI earns its place at the top of that conversation for a few specific reasons:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Motion fluidity.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Kling's outputs move the way things actually move. Physics feels real. Objects have weight. This sounds basic, but it is the hardest problem in AI video, and Kling solves it better than most.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Face consistency.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If your video features a person, the face stays the same across the entire clip. No morphing, no uncanny shifts. This alone makes Kling AI viable for professional marketing content.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Scene coherence.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Backgrounds, lighting, and spatial relationships remain stable throughout the generated clip. The AI understands depth and perspective in a way that many competitors still struggle with.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Audio-visual sync.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The built-in audio generation is a genuine differentiator. Generating video and audio together in a single pipeline eliminates a step that creators on other platforms have to handle manually.",
            "marks": []
          }
