        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, Kling AI offers a free tier that lets you generate a limited number of video clips. This is perfect for testing the platform and seeing the output quality before committing to a paid plan. Paid pricing starts at approximately $0.084 per second of standard-quality video.",
            "marks": []
