        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Kling AI supports both text-to-video and image-to-video generation. You can upload a photo, illustration, or any reference image, and the AI will animate it with natural, coherent motion while preserving the original composition and details.",
            "marks": []
          }
