        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What makes Kling AI different from other AI video generators?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kling AI stands out for three key reasons: motion fluidity that respects real-world physics, consistent face rendering across frames, and built-in audio generation. The combination of these capabilities in a single platform — with API access and transparent per-second pricing — makes it one of the most complete AI video tools available.",
